          <h3>Do I have to buy anything?</h3>

          <p>No. MultiBit Merchant is free for you to take away and use. Its purpose is to help others to grow the Bitcoin economy so that the world
          may benefit from more efficient trade.</p>
          
          <p>However, you should know that I offer a managed service so that merchants can focus on running their business without the hassle of running their own IT infrastructure. By offering a fixed subscription model based on traffic, and no transaction fees, I believe that most merchants will find it easier to do business with bitcoins through MultiBit Merchant than by any other means.</p>
          
        </div>

