          <h3>What does your company stand for?</h3>

          <p>We want to bring back privacy to the online world. We want to be able to buy something and not wonder if there is
          an enormous database about all our purchases being sold to the highest bidder. If we want to buy something anonymously,
          we want to be sure that the merchant we're dealing with respects that. MultiBit Merchant makes that happen.</p>

          <p>We want to enable people to think for themselves. It is fine to work for a company that respects you and pays you
          accordingly, it is another to be forced to work at something that makes you miserable. There are great opportunities out
          there, and sometimes we all need a lift to get us started. MultiBit Merchant can help <strong>you</strong> get started, and then keep
          you going by connecting you with other people who can help.</p>

